"Saturday Bowl"

3
00:00:14,240 --> 00:00:17,440
Aku berjaya! Strike!

4
00:00:17,440 --> 00:00:18,840
Itulah kau, Ran!

5
00:00:18,840 --> 00:00:20,140
Kau hebat!

6
00:00:20,140 --> 00:00:23,740
Aku kesal tentang permainan tenis, tapi bowling juga menyenangkan!

7
00:00:23,740 --> 00:00:26,440
Yah, ada seorang pria yang kesal karena tidak bisa

8
00:00:26,440 --> 00:00:30,340
