00:16:47,253 --> 00:16:49,453
Inspektur Yamamura!

301
00:16:49,453 --> 00:16:51,853
Ada lebam yang ditemukan pada perut korban.

302
00:16:51,853 --> 00:16:54,053
Lebam?

303
00:16:54,053 --> 00:16:56,053
Benar.

304
00:16:56,053 --> 00:16:59,153
Itu mungkin perbuatan aku.

305
00:16:59,153 --> 00:17:02,053
Karena dia mabuk dan mencari masalah denganku,

306
00:17:02,053 --> 00:17:04,053
