00:20:04,553 --> 00:20:05,953
Nanti!

371
00:20:05,953 --> 00:20:07,953
Aku bilang tunggu!

372
00:20:11,153 --> 00:20:12,853
Hampir saja.

373
00:20:12,853 --> 00:20:15,953
Tempat ini kelihatan sedikit miring.

