376
00:20:21,153 --> 00:20:24,853
Mereka bilang akan memperbaikinya mulai bulan depan.

377
00:20:24,853 --> 00:20:26,553
Oh, begitu.

378
00:20:26,553 --> 00:20:28,553
Penurunan tanah...

379
00:20:28,553 --> 00:20:31,753
Tunggu sebentar. Jika begitu...

380
00:20:31,753 --> 00:20:36,053
