403
00:21:49,753 --> 00:21:52,853
Meskipun pintunya ditutup, ini tidak akan berhasil.

404
00:21:52,853 --> 00:21:54,553
Benar.

405
00:21:54,553 --> 00:21:56,153
Di samping itu,

406
00:21:56,153 --> 00:21:59,653
